  <p>
    PR Review Kit works with 18 AI IDEs. The installer configures the correct files for each IDE
    automatically. How you start the agent depends on your IDE type.
  </p>

  <h2 id="how">How agents work per IDE</h2>
  <p>
    Different IDEs have different ways to invoke AI agents. The installer handles this for you, but
    it helps to understand the three main patterns:
  </p>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Slash commands</strong> — type <code>/prr-master</code> in the chat input</li>
    <li><strong>Workflow panel</strong> — open the Workflows panel and select <code>prr-master</code></li>
    <li><strong>Custom modes or references</strong> — IDE-specific approach (see below)</li>
  </ul>

  <h2 id="slash">Slash command IDEs</h2>
  <p>Type <code>/prr-master</code> in the AI chat to open the full review menu, or <code>/prr-quick</code> to run the full pipeline automatically.</p>
